{"type": "article", "id": 2931, "title": "Versace & DISARONNO 联名鸡尾酒包装", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-20T08:34:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232409gWavrsEN4VHJ01dR.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tVersace 日前联手意大利酒品牌 DISARONNO 带来了一款特别的酒瓶包装，蓝色与金色的混搭图纹设计凸显出 Versace 的高贵质感，搭配以真正的金箔。DISARONNO 为了这个联名产品还专门制作了一款鸡尾酒 DISARONNO Versace Sour 。值得一提的是，Versace 与 DISARONNO 准备将这款联名作品的一部分收入捐给慈善项目 Fashion 4 Development ，希望能够通过这样的方式推广非洲地区的妇女解放意识。定价 39 欧元，<a href=\"http://www.sotostore.com/store/disaronno-versace-special-edition-bottle\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232407ZziuR82jAoS70BQK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232408fNOT3D9cQvde57Jj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232408YVBCraH5FO2pqLi3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2265625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232408dUEP1rTQ2i8MV6qL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2265625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}